column2: Trade Guards of the Solemn Desert

The despotism of the Titans is a complex centralized bureaucratic system in which numerous temple and castle lands belong to the sole tyrant - Lugal. Lugal manages a vast bureaucratic and military apparatus of governors and officials who ensure that the country is governed by Lugal through military force or the dependence of his subjects on centrally allocated resources. This type of government is supported by the scholastics of the Cult of Knowledge, who consider it the optimal form of government in the current era, but the direct vassals of Lugal may thinks otherwise...
